    - Added `generate-github-links.js` to append GitHub commit links to the generated JSON data.
    - Created `get-daily-commit-range.sh` to calculate the commit range from yesterday 8 AM to today 8 AM based on timezone offset.
    - Developed GitHub Actions workflow `daily-git-report.yml` to automate the daily report generation and PR creation.
